csci331.team.red.dao

Class CharacterDAO

  • java.lang.Object
    • csci331.team.red.dao.CharacterDAO
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CharacterRepository

    public class CharacterDAO
extends java.lang.Object
    CSCI331T MW SUPERCLASS

    CharacterDAO is the superclass of CharacterRepository. CharacterDAO was created as a superclass as it randomly creates characters from database data. It also contains several global variables, that are needed by other classes.
    Author:
    melany
